üî• CCEE QUICK MEMORY (HIGH-YIELD)
HIPAA = US Healthcare Data Law (Mandatory)
PHI / ePHI = Core focus
Rules = Privacy | Security | Breach Notification | Enforcement
Safeguards = Administrative + Physical + Technical
